  "description": "Freight Bridge LLC is a trusted moving and freight hauling company based in Iowa City, Iowa. As an authorized interstate carrier (USDOT 4414774, MC-1734786), we handle residential and commercial moves, haul freight in all 50 states for brokers and dispatchers with our own truck, and provide post-construction hauling for data center projects in the Iowa City and Cedar Rapids corridor. Our experienced team is hands-on with every job.",
